      • fulfillNodesWithFiles

        private void fulfillNodesWithFiles(java.util.List<FileObject> fileList,
                         java.util.Map<java.lang.String,NodeInfo> accessMap,
                         java.util.List<NodeInfo> nodes)
        Add files to NodeInfo objects. Firstly, files with single access defined will be added to their nodes. If master has only access to some files and does not participate to computing, files will be distributed to another nodes evenly. Files that multiple nodes may access will be distributed to nodes by minimum queue length
        Parameters:
        xmlFileList - file List to add
        accessMap - other nodes mapped by hostname string
        nodes - list of all nodes
